"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-30-little-olympian-fencer-says-competed-paris-heavily-pregnant\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS,\\u00a0France\\u00a0(AFP) - Egyptian fencer Nada Hafez has revealed she competed at the Paris Olympics, reaching the last 16 in her event and defeating a higher-ranked rival on the way, while seven months\\u00a0pregnant.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hafez, a three-time Olympian from Cairo, ranked 26th, beat American fencer Elizabeth Tartakovsky in the sabre event before succumbing to Hayoung Jeon of South Korea in the quarter finals on Monday.\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\", \"score\": 0.7769010711699723, \"rank\": 0.2871651708421206, \"text\": \"Hafez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999992587898323, \"rank\": 7.412106903329571e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cairo\", \"score\": 0.9999988363756478, \"rank\": 9.828980078705123e-07, \"text\": \"Cairo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cairo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cairo\"}, {\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999965975147138, \"rank\": 3.1530181236940583e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 285, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.942170065929571, \"rank\": 0.03311757184507426, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oh_Ha-young\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hayoung\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oh_Ha-young\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oh_Ha-young\"}, {\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999827642148549, \"rank\": 1.241365846410003e-05, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Three times *Olympian* but this time carrying a little Olympian!\\\"\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999992587898323, \"rank\": 7.412106903329571e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 465, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999992587898323, \"rank\": 7.412106903329571e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"the 26-year-old said on Instagram late Monday.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7419930625300596e-19, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What appears to you as two players\\u2026 they were actually three!\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was me, my competitor, and my yet-to-come to our world, little baby!\\\"\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she wrote in English.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She previously competed in Rio in 2016 and in the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Games in 2021 in the highly demanding sabre, a slashing weapon which demands lightning speed and reflexes from competitors.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999839436347723, \"rank\": 1.6056623116706426e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hafez said she was proud to have secured her place in the round of 16 at the Grand Palais.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\", \"score\": 0.7769010711699723, \"rank\": 0.2871651708421206, \"text\": \"Hafez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The rollercoaster of pregnancy is tough on its own, but having to fight to keep the balance of life & sports was nothing short of strenuous, however worth it,\\\" she wrote.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her Instagram post has racked up more than 25,000 likes, with many praising the athlete.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Balancing between pregnancy and pursuing your passion is never easy, so you should be super proud of yourself regardless of the outcome,\\\" one user said.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just amazing,\\\" added another.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But is it not cheating to fence two against one?\\\"\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"the user joked.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the athlete was also trolled by sexist comments from some users who suggested she should not have competed while\\u00a0pregnant\\u00a0and insinuating this had affected her performance for her country.\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hafez began fencing at age 11 in Egypt.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\", \"score\": 0.7769010711699723, \"rank\": 0.2871651708421206, \"text\": \"Hafez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hafez\"}, {\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"score\": 0.8049463805071903, \"rank\": 0.2420911069351222, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I first took up swimming and gymnastics, but then I had to leave gymnastics and I joined fencing by chance,\\\" she said in comments released by the International Fencing Federation.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration_Internationale_d'Escrime\", \"score\": 0.9999999998710791, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Fencing Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration_Internationale_d'Escrime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration_Internationale_d'Escrime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt like I wanted to try it after seeing my friend and once I did, I loved it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": []}]}"